channel.title: How popular is your server?
channel.description:
Well I was checking out google and I just wanted to see something. So I started typing in "davidsc" and all of a sudden 5 of the 10 suggested inputs were about my source/server. I was like "woah"! So I searced davidscape and all of the results were related to my source/server.
So My Question: How much of your server/source's name must you type in for the first suggested input to be yours?
Mine: Davidsca/Davidscape (8/10 - 80%)

So My Question: How much of your server/source’s name must you type in for the [b]first[b] suggested input to be yours?
